General.Name: Peel Mining Limited
General.Description: Peel Mining Limited engages in the exploration of base and precious metals in the Cobar Region of New South Wales, Australia. The company explores for copper, zinc, lead, silver, gold, and tungsten deposits. Its flagship project is the Mallee Bull copper project comprising an area of 85 square kilometers located in the central New South Wales. The company was incorporated in 2006 and is headquartered in West Perth, Australia.
